arts.ttl: Orlando City 4–1 Inter Miami: Takeaways From Worrying Florida Derby Defeat
arts.sum: Orlando City swept Inter Miami in regular season action after a 3–0 win in their reverse fixture in May.

arts.ttl: Orlando City 4-1 Inter Miami: Player Ratings As Lions Dominate Herons in Florida Derby
arts.sum: Orlando began the scoring early with a second-minute goal from Luis Muriel, before Miami’s Yannick Bright drew the visitors level with a wonder-strike from the top of the box in the fifth minute. Things got even worse for the Herons in the final moments, as Benjamin Cremaschi barely kept Marco Pašalić onside, allowing the Orlando attacker to break through and extend the match to 4–1.

arts.ttl: Luis Muriel and Martín Ojeda propel Orlando City to 4-1 victory over Inter Miami
arts.sum: Luis Muriel scored a goal in each half and Martín Ojeda had a goal and an assist to lead Orlando City to a 4-1 victory over Inter Miami on Sunday night. Orlando City took a 2-1 lead five minutes into the second half on Muriel’s unassisted eighth goal of the season.

arts.ttl: Inter Miami 4–1 Orlando City: Player Ratings As Lions Dominate Herons in Florida Derby
arts.sum: Luis Muriel scored twice for Orlando City SC as the Lions swept the season series between the Florida clubs.

arts.ttl: Orlando City SC vs. Inter Miami: Preview, Predictions and Lineups
arts.sum: The two Leagues Cup quarterfinalists battle in MLS play for the second time this season.

arts.ttl: Inter Miami Predicted Lineup vs. Orlando City: De Paul Set for MLS Debut
arts.sum: Lionel Messi won’t be available for the Florida derby due to an injury sustained during Leagues Cup.
